    ImperfectMaze
    This class ImperfectMaze extends PerfectMaze and creates a maze that is not perfect, meaning it can have some loops or extra walls.
    ImperfectMazeKruskal
    This class ImperfectMazeKruskal extends PerfectMaze and creates an imperfect maze using Kruskal's algorithm first to generate a perfect maze.
    LabyrinthApp
    LabyrinthApp is the class to display the labyrinth using JavaFX and interact with the user.
    MainInteract
     
    Solver
    Solver class provides different algorithms to solve a maze: - BFS (Breadth-First Search) - DFS (Depth-First Search) - A* algorithm - Dijkstra algorithm - Wall follower (left and right) It also tracks the time taken for each solving attempt.
    SolverSbS
    SolverSbS class provides step-by-step maze solving with different algorithms.
